Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.29,0:22:22.48,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}许个愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:25.62,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}最爱的那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.62,0:22:31.85,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}一定满溢着光芒
